RECEIVER'S SALE - AN EDUCATED INVESTMENT IN 18 STUDENT APARTMENTS IN A COMPLEX OF 83 APARTMENTS
 
CBRE Hotels, instructed by Ian Purchas of SV Partners as Receiver and Manager of Global House Investments Pty Ltd (Receiver and Manager Appointed) and Barkly Place Investments Pty Ltd (Receiver and Manager Appointed), are pleased to present to the market 18 strata-titled student accommodation apartments as part of Global House - 24 Barkly Place in Carlton, Victoria. 

This modern, purpose-built student accommodation facility is located in an excellent position within Melbourne's recognised education precinct and is just a short walk to The University of Melbourne, The Royal Melbourne Institute of Technology and the Melbourne CBD's vast array of retail shopping along with food and beverage outlets.

Key investment highlights include:  

•	18 strata-titled student accommodation units to be sold in one line
•	Fully leased and furnished (excepting one unit remaining vacant for inspections)
•	A mix of four types of unit (Standard, Medium, Large Studio, Large Studio with Balcony)
•	Spacious ground floor reception, lounge area and courtyard
•	Attractive rooftop deck with city views

For Sale via Expressions of Interest.
